 <text id="F3057T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus describes his regiment's movement from Jacksonville, Florida, to Morris Island, South
     Carolina. He also urges his wife to stop working as soon as he can send her his army pay.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1864-04-18"><orig reg="April">Aprile</orig> the 18th 1864</date>
      <name type="place"><orig reg="Morris">Morres</orig>
       <orig reg="island">iland</orig> South <orig reg="Carolina">Carlina</orig></name>
     </dateline>
     <salute>Dear</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>i take this present <orig reg="time">tim</orig> to <orig reg="write">rite</orig> you <orig
      reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">fu</orig> lines to let you <orig reg="know">now</orig> that i am Well at
     present and i hope <orig reg="When">Whean</orig>
     <orig reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">fu</orig> lines reach you <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="may">ma</orig>
     <orig reg="find">finde</orig> you in the same state of <orig reg="health">healte</orig> i <orig
      reg="thought">thot</orig> i <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="write">rite</orig> and let you <orig reg="know">now</orig> that We <orig reg="have"
      >heafe</orig> move move back to morris <orig reg="island">iland</orig> and We <orig reg="left"
      >lefte</orig>
     <orig reg="Jacksonville">Jack svill</orig> on the 14th of <orig reg="April">Aprile</orig> and
     We landed <orig reg="here">hear</orig> last <orig reg="night">nighte</orig> it <orig reg="rain"
      >rane</orig> all day and all <orig reg="night">nighte</orig> but <orig reg="our">ar</orig>
     <orig reg="Colonel">Curel</orig> got us in to <orig reg="houses">hoses</orig> to stay all <orig
      reg="night">nighte</orig> and he <orig reg="Went">Wente</orig> and <orig reg="bought"
     >bote</orig> a <orig reg="whole">hole</orig> lot of <unclear>Can</unclear>
     <unclear>sope</unclear> and We had a <orig reg="great">grate</orig>
     <orig reg="supper">super</orig> and then i strips <orig reg="off">of</orig>
     <orig reg="my">mi</orig> Wet <orig reg="Clothes">Close</orig> and <orig reg="Went">Wente</orig>
     to bed and i <orig reg="Could">Cod</orig> not <orig reg="sleep">seape</orig>
     <orig reg="much">mutch</orig> but i got <orig reg="up">oup</orig> in the <orig reg="morning"
      >mornen</orig> and i fell a <orig reg="little">littel</orig> bad but as <orig reg="soon"
     >son</orig> as i got <orig reg="my">mi</orig>
     <orig reg="Clothes">Close</orig>
     <orig reg="dried">dride</orig> i felt better i <orig reg="Can't">Cant</orig> tell how how long
     i Will bear <orig reg="here">hear</orig> but you Can <orig reg="write">rite</orig> as <orig
      reg="soon">son</orig> as you Can and direct <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letter to morris <orig
      reg="island">iland</orig> south <orig reg="Carolina">Carlina</orig> i Wish that you <orig
      reg="Would">Wod</orig> let me <orig reg="know">now</orig>
     <orig reg="Where">Whear</orig> John has to move <orig reg="to">tow</orig> and let me <orig
      reg="know">now</orig> how large the <orig reg="house">hose</orig> is <orig reg="for"
     >fer</orig> if i <orig reg="don't">donte</orig> get <orig reg="home">hom</orig> in a <orig
      reg="short">sort</orig>
     <orig reg="time">tim</orig>
     <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i <orig reg="Want">Wante</orig> you to go and stay With John <orig
      reg="for">fer</orig> i Will be <orig reg="paid">pade</orig>
     <orig reg="off">of</orig> in a <orig reg="short">sorte</orig>
     <orig reg="time">tim</orig> and then i Want you to <orig reg="stop">stope</orig> Working out
      <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i <orig reg="know">now</orig> that you <orig reg="Can't">Cant</orig>
     <orig reg="stand">stande</orig> it <orig reg="much">mutch</orig> longer and <orig reg="they"
      >tha</orig> have move us out of the <unclear>deaner</unclear>
     <orig reg="until">untill</orig> We get <orig reg="paid">pade</orig>
     <orig reg="off">of</orig> or be sent home and if <orig reg="they">tha</orig> pay us <orig
      reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i Will send it all home i had <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig>
     <orig reg="some">som</orig>
     <orig reg="two">tow</orig> or <orig reg="three">the</orig> letter but <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="said">sed</orig> that <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig> not go <orig reg="without">with out</orig>
     <orig reg="post">poaste</orig> stamps and i had <orig reg="none">non</orig> to <orig reg="put"
      >poot</orig> on them and i hope that you Will send me <orig reg="some">som</orig> if you Can
     get them and if you <orig reg="Can't">Cante</orig>
     <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> you must <orig reg="write">rite</orig> often i now must bring <orig
      reg="my">mi</orig> letter to a Close <orig reg="by">bi</orig>
     <orig reg="bidding">biden</orig> you good <orig reg="night">nighte</orig> nothing more at
     present but still <orig reg="remain">remane</orig></p>

    <closer>
     <salute><orig reg="your">yor</orig> Dear <orig reg="husband">husben</orig></salute>
     <signed>David</signed>
     <seg type="postscript">David Demus to <orig reg="Mary">Marry</orig> Demus</seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
